OL,3,CMartin Lewis campaign to stop
OL,4,C'grotesque' council tax collection
OL,6,FMartin Lewis heads a new campaign to
OL,7,Fpush for a change in council tax debt
OL,8,Fcollection policy, ITV News' Consumer
OL,9,FEditor Chris Choi reports
OL,11,FNew research provided to ITV News has
OL,12,Fhighlighted the impact of council tax
OL,13,Fdebt collection methods.
OL,15,FThe Money and Mental Health Policy
OL,16,FInstitute, a charity founded by Martin
OL,17,FLewis, published figures that reveal a
OL,18,Fdaunting pathway from debt to despair
OL,19,Ffor many people.
