OL,3,CMartin Lewis campaign to stop
OL,4,C'grotesque' council tax collection
OL,6,FMr Lewis, known to millions through
OL,7,Fhis money saving TV and radio
OL,8,Fappearances, is heading the new
OL,9,Fcampaign to push for a change of
OL,10,Fpolicy.
OL,12,FAt present, anyone missing a single
OL,13,Finstalment can be required to pay
OL,14,Ftheir full annual council tax bill,
OL,15,Fwhich is typically just over #1,600.
OL,17,FFor the majority of households this
OL,18,Fwould be a terror, but for those with
OL,19,Fmental health problems, things can
OL,20,Fspiral into far more than a financial
OL,21,Fmeltdown.
