OL,3,CMartin Lewis campaign to stop
OL,4,C'grotesque' council tax collection
OL,6,FMr Lewis told us: "Council tax
OL,7,Fcollection practices are so aggressive
OL,8,Fthey'd make the banks blush.
OL,10,F"The grotesque process couldn't have
OL,11,Fbeen designed better to accelerate
OL,12,Fdistress for people in council tax
OL,13,Fdebt"
OL,15,FThe new research shows that around 10%
OL,16,Fof people with mental health problems
OL,17,Fare behind with council tax.
OL,19,FThat's compared with around 4% of the
OL,20,Fgeneral population.
