OL,3,CMartin Lewis campaign to stop
OL,4,C'grotesque' council tax collection
OL,6,FWe put these points to a spokesperson
OL,7,Ffor local councils, Cllr Peter
OL,8,FMarlands of the Local Government
OL,9,FAssociation, who said: "Where councils
OL,10,Fcan help and do help is where somebody
OL,11,Fhas missed council tax they can
OL,12,Fcollect it in a considerate way".
OL,14,FLocal authorities say they work hard
OL,15,Fto support the vulnerable but are
OL,16,Funder a duty to collect tax.
